sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Chat Plugin
    participant H as Hub Instance
    participant S as MCP Server
    C->>H: call_tool()
    H->>H: Check Ready
    alt Not Ready
        H-->>C: Error: Not Ready
    end
    H->>S: POST /tools
    S-->>H: Tool Result
    H-->>C: Return Result
    Note over C,S: Similar flow for resources
    
    C->>H: access_resource()
    H->>H: Check Ready
    H->>S: POST /resources
    S-->>H: Resource Data
    H-->>C: Return Data
